              <ownedComment xmi:id="_1S66sJaxEey_Oso2woJSWA">
                <body>A concrete Paint Strategy to draw a composite shape of Fish with upright implementation.
@author Son Nguyen and Cole Rabson</body>
              </ownedComment>
              <generalization xmi:id="_1SjHQpaxEey_Oso2woJSWA" general="_1Q_BAJaxEey_Oso2woJSWA"/>
